snippet.title: Sim Theme Park gameplay (PC Game, 1999)
snippet.description:
Gameplay for Sim Theme Park (aka theme park world), PC game produced by Electronic Arts in 1999 - http://www.squakenet.com/download/sim-theme-park-iso/14408/
Building up a new park in this excellent simulation following the success given by Theme Park game.
Played through old Windows XP real machine.
Recorded with original sound.

Similar videos you may like:
Theme Park - https://youtu.be/RnzYaubKeI0
RollerCoaster Tycoon - https://youtu.be/JNjpS2fZZRo
